// Test group: syntax
// Test purpose: showing the simplest syntax for a region
//
// Test description:
// 440.wav will play in the whole keyboard, no looping
//
// If the .sfz file is in the same folder than the samples,
// the path is not required. For instance:
// 
// sample=440.wav
//
// Otherwise, path must be specified -relative- to the .sfz file location.
// This example file will try to load the sample 440.wav
// from a folder called '[ samples ]' located in its parent folder.
//
// ....\..\samples\
// ....\..\samples\440.wav
// ....\00 - syntax\
// ....\00 - syntax\syntax introduction.sfz


<region> sample=..\..\samples\440.wav